name: Pdiff
tagline: A better diffing tool written in Node.js

# pdiff [![Build Status](https://travis-ci.org/HiroakiMikami/pdiff.svg?branch=master)](https://travis-ci.org/HiroakiMikami/pdiff)
## Install
```bash
$ npm -g install pdiff
```

## Usage
### Command Line Tool
```bash
$ pdiff <file1> <file2>
```

### API
Not yet.
